<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔大吃了一惊。“罗西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔知道了她的秘密。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她深吸了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……嗨，特勒尔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔睁大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我早就知道了，罗西！我早知道你是火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”罗西说得很慢，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，你听好了。你不能告诉任何人，知道吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有另外两个人知道。潘校长和布洛姆市长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔一只手按在胸口上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证保密！”他看了看四周，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里发生了什么事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我正在和布洛姆市长打电话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间，有什么东西把所有的孩子和老师都吸走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道那是什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么和布洛姆市长打电话？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城监狱发生了一件奇怪的事情。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在还不能告诉你。我得马上赶到那里去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我留在这里，也许还能找到一些线索。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点点头。“好主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你需要我，你可以打电话到我的手表上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西给了特勒尔火箭女孩儿的特殊号码 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把号码存进了自己的手机里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了美罗城监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看到大楼的一侧有一个大洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从洞里飞进监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！你吓了我一跳！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，侦探先生。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很急。除了这个洞，早上还发生了别的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还发生了什么事？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西告诉了他学校发生的事件。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摸了摸下巴。“嗯……两个非常奇怪的事件。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您觉得这两件事件有关联吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>侦探叹了一口气。“我不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，威格尔斯夫人从床上坐起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌睡觉时间！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转动了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在是早上，威格尔斯夫人。不是睡觉时间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长说所有的犯人都在这儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狱警已经数过几次犯人了。所有人都在。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是谁弄出的这个洞？为什么这么做呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西仔细看了一下那个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“洞的内部表面非常光滑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看不到一点儿墙壁的碎块。太奇怪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌睡觉时间！”威格尔斯夫人再次说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转过头去。“现在不是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我讨厌睡觉时间！我讨厌睡觉时间！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人的耳朵里冒出一小股烟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好奇怪啊！”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用眼睛发射的x射线看威格尔斯夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这个坏人的身体里面，她看到了齿轮和弹簧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大吃了一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是威格尔斯夫人！那是一个机器人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>